{"tid":873385,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不用分那麼細？ 亞青盃南韓賽事誤播北韓國歌","createTime":"2018-10-23T11:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T12:40:04.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7608802e4c6bf253499cc483d5e85d70ce16873c","tid":873385,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181022/large/1540221156_fa60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181022%2Flarge%2F1540221156_fa60.jpg&h=2ed92aab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">南韓教練露出大惑不解的表情</span><br />\n<br />\n自從南韓總統文在寅上場之後，南北韓關係大有改善，「文金會」已是第二度舉行，兩國更計劃一同申辦2032年奧運。可能受這個溫馨的氛圍影響，昨日亞青盃C組南韓對約旦的賽事就上演一個世紀大「蝦碌」，賽會誤將北韓國歌當成南韓國歌播，南韓教練都露出大惑不解的表情。據韓聯社周二報道，南韓足協已向比賽監督表達了不滿，並已正式就此事向亞足聯投訴。<br />\n<br />\n亞青盃正在印尼舉行，日本為上屆冠軍。其實南北韓的國歌都有著同一個名字，兩首歌都是《愛國歌》，雖然比較相似，但旋律與歌風都不太相同。從鏡頭中可見，當賽會播錯歌之後，兩名南韓教練疑惑地向後方張望，更奇怪的是，有南韓球員跟住北韓國歌一齊唱。<br />\n<br />\n好彩賽會之後都意識到出錯，連忙改播南韓國歌，化解尷尬的場面。南韓最終以3:1擊敗約旦，兩戰1勝1和得4分暫排小組第1。其實這樣的錯誤並不是第一次發生，在2012年倫敦奧運北韓對哥倫比亞的女足賽事，當賽會介紹球員時，屏幕顯示的畫面竟將南韓國旗當成北韓國旗，北韓女足球員即離場抗議，之後才返回場內作賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181022/large/1540221270_899c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181022%2Flarge%2F1540221270_899c.jpg&h=fa3450c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">南韓球員(右)唱錯歌</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181023/58824122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181023%2F58824122&d=YHjfK%2BayDGKMcIDSFjaTjwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=f7a6ca40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181023%2F58824122&h=3fde8a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181023/58824122</a>"},{"pid":"21cd27468d7f753690dacdec94e52d805aa746e7","tid":873385,"uid":41245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"屌你啲球員一樣樣嘅"},{"pid":"b0d55229845d88ae94cdb7d5c6b4fcc0ba62cbe8","tid":873385,"uid":171786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"21cd27468d7f753690dacdec94e52d805aa746e7","tid":873385,"uid":41245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"屌你啲球員一樣樣嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人造人唔止娛樂界先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37a37d1c048e06e98064a35996b66dd460c4667","tid":873385,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"哈薩克果獲先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}